text: Ted Noble (16 January 1865 - 4 May 1941) was an Australian cricketer. He played seven first-class matches for New South Wales in 1893/94. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1865 births Category:1941 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
